title: Office 365 Saturday
sessionTitle: Come here power users! See cool goodies in SharePoint 2016, PowerApps. Microsoft Flow and Power BI
eventShortDescription: SSW is live with SharePoint 2016 and to me, this is the most exciting release ever! Jeff Teper, the boss of SharePoint, is back and you can definitely feel it in the latest feature announcements. I see cohesion in the announced features, a vision of connecting people with their data both organizational and personal, on all devices, in the cloud, on-premises and all done with the elegance of a modern web UI. Let’s focus on a few of the newest cool pieces: PowerBI and PowerApps, let’s see what these do and how awesome they are.​

SSW is live with SharePoint 2016 and to me, this is the most exciting release ever! Jeff Teper, the boss of SharePoint, is back and you can definitely feel it in the latest feature announcements. I see cohesion in the announced features, a vision of connecting people with their data both organizational and personal, on all devices, in the cloud, on-premises and all done with the elegance of a modern web UI.
